King called Ivan the Fool and said:<br>-If you don't bring me two talking birds tomorrow, I will cut your head off.<br>Ivan brought owl and sparrow. King said:<br>-Let them say something.<br>Ivan asks:<br>-How much did vodka cost before?<br>Sparrow:<br>-Chirik<br>Ivan to owl:<br>-And you, owl, confirm.<br>Owl:<br>-Confirm.